---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Why Beautiful Matters
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In a world of markdown mess and platform wars, beauty is revolutionary.

CDF exists because we believe documents should be beautiful by default. Not
because we're designers or perfectionists, but because beauty makes things
easier to read, understand, and remember.

When you copy from Cursor and paste into Notion, it should just work. When
you open a document in Mac Notes, it should look beautiful. When you share
a document, it should preserve its formatting.

This is not about perfection. This is about respect.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  The Philosophy
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CDF is built on three principles:

  - Beauty by default, not as an afterthought
  - Universal compatibility, not platform lock-in
  - AI-friendly structure, not human-only format

We don't choose between beauty and functionality. We choose both.

We don't choose between platforms. We choose all of them.

We don't choose between humans and AI. We choose both.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  The Vision
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Imagine a world where:

  - Every document is beautiful
  - Formatting never breaks
  - Copy/paste just works
  - AI understands structure
  - Documents are free forever

This is the world CDF is building.

Join us. Let's make documents beautiful again.

